[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……さて。動画投稿サイトでのバズを\n狙ったようですが、どうです？　再生数の状況は",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00590",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ダントツで勝ってるよ！\n……『ＱＥジーンズ』が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00591",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "やはり一筋縄ではいかないでありまするなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00592",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ネタみたいな動画はいいわよ。\nでも、なんで歌とかダンスの動画も負けてるの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00593",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "絶対にこっちのほうがクオリティ高いのに……\nみんな目が節穴なんじゃない！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00594",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そもそも、歌やダンスを評価したい、なんて視聴者は\n思っていないのですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00595",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "刺激のあるもの、明日の話題にできるもの。\nそういった即物的な娯楽を求めているのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00596",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "やっぱり、動画の内容がいい子に\nまとまりすぎてるのかなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00597",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "次はそれぞれの個性を活かしつつ、\nもっとエンタメに寄った内容を検討いたしましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00598",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ふん。なんだか、納得いかない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00599",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まあまあ。残り時間は限られているでござるが、\nやれるだけのことはやってみましょう、ヨハナ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00600",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "思いっきり考えを変えるのもいいかも。\n誰か有名な人とコラボした動画を出してみるとか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00601",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それこそ、社長の力でなんとかならないの？\n有名なスターが何人も所属してるんでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00602",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そんなおんぶにだっこされるなんて、私は嫌。\n悔しいじゃない。私たち自身には魅力がないみたいで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00603",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "プライドが高すぎても良くありませんが、\nこれに関してはヨハナと同じく賛同いたしませんわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00604",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "力量の釣り合わない相手とのコラボは、\nどうしても「意図」が感じられてしまうもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00605",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そういう面でのクリーンなイメージは大事ですわ。\n特に、アイドルに関しては",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00606",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そっか……そうだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00607",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！　やっぱり自分たちの力で頑張ろう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00608",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "たとえ審査に受からずとも、こうして努力した結果は\n確実にファンを増やしていまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00609",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "みんな、気負いすぎず、でござるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00610",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]